default.title: default
steps: 1. Apply foundation all over face
2. Apply concealer to under eyes and any problem areas
3. Apply blush to apples of cheeks
4. Apply eyeshadow
5. Apply eyeliner
7. Apply mascara
8. Apply lipstick

result1.title: edgy
steps: 1. Apply foundation all over face
2. Apply concealer to under eyes and any problem areas
3. Apply heavy blush to apples of cheeks
4. Apply darker eyeshadow colors to eyelid and fade towards crease
5. Apply lighter eyeshadow to inner corner and below eyebrows
6. Apply heavy eyeliner, wing tip optional
7. Apply mascara
8. Apply dark lipstick

result2.title: casual
steps: 1. Apply foundation all over face
2. Apply concealer to under eyes and any problem areas
3. Apply light blush to apples of cheeks
4. Apply light/medium eyeshadow all over crease
5. Apply light eyeshadow to inner crease and below eyebrows
6. Apply eyeliner to waterline if desired
7. Apply mascara

result3.title: rogue
steps: 1. Apply foundation all over face
2. Apply concealer to under eyes and any problem areas
3. Apply heavy blush to apples of cheeks
4. Apply your craziest eyeshadow heavily to your lids
5. Apply thick line of black or other colored eyeliner to top lid
6. Extend eyeliner out into a creative wing
7. Apply mascara to top and bottom lashes, using multiple coats to build
